column6:
@Bose 1/ Really disappointed with Bose ending cloud support for the SoundTouch 20.

I bought this as a premium connected speaker system, not just a basic Bluetooth speaker.

Now Bose has effectively stripped away key functionality from a product customers paid hundreds for.

